withdrawal threat and confident to win a majority in the
parliament which will resume its session Thursday next week.
</P>
<P>
AIADMK holds 18 seats in the parliament and a withdrawal of
support to the BJP would put the coalition government to a serious
test of winning a majority in the parliament. 
