<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Closes Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, April 6 (Xinhua) -- The Tunis Stock Exchange index
closed at 569.30 points Monday, down 0.42 percent from Monday's
finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 93,022 shares changed hands in 254 deals,
with the turnover reaching 2,373,701 dinars (2,157,910 U.S.
dollars). 
