<HEADLINE> Botswana Grants Asylum for 1,116 Namibians </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, April 6 (Xinhua) -- Botswana has granted asylum
to a further 1,116 Namibian secessionists, who fled to Botswana
between October and December last year, South African Press
Association (SAPA) reported Tuesday.
