them to the U.S. authorities," Kyprianou said.
</P>
<P>
He said it is a purely humanitarian mission. "I hope it will
succeed and pave the way for peaceful developments," he said.
</P>
<P>
He said he has asked for a 24-hour cease-fire in Yugoslavia in
order to conclude his mission successfully.
</P>
<P>
The three U.S. soldiers were captured last week near the
Yugoslav-Macedonian border. 
