<HEADLINE> Yugoslavia Should Try Harder for Peace: UK's Cook </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, April 7 (Xinhua) -- British Foreign Secretary Robin
Cook said on Wednesday that Yugoslav President Slobodan Milosevic
should have to "try harder" if he wanted peace.
</P>
<P>
