<P>
Samaranch said that he was glad that Beijing decided to bid for
the Olympic Games for the second time and expressed his wish that
it would succeed.
</P>
<P>
CNOC President Wu Shaozu, present at the talks, said that his
organization fully supports Beijing's bidding.
</P>
<P>
Beijing took part in the contest for the 2000 Games in the
early 1990's. 
</P>
