<HEADLINE> Xinhua World Economic News Summary at 0500 GMT, April 7 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON -- The Conference Board said Tuesday that the Index
of Leading Economic Indicators climbed 0.2 percent, for a fifth
straight month, in February.
</P>
